Abstract: NEW YORK  GOVERNMENT OFFICES  Closed.  POST OFFICE  Closed except for main post office at 33rd Street and Eighth Avenue.  BANKS  Closed.  PARKING  Alternate-side regulations suspended. No-parking zone extends from West 34th Street to West 59th Street between the Avenue of the Americas and Eighth Avenue.  SANITATION  Normal pickups for garbage and recycling. No street cleanings.  TRANSPORTATION  City buses and subways on a Saturday schedule  with additional service. Long Island Rail Road on weekend schedule with additional trains. Metro-North on a holiday schedule with extra trains.
